=== 票房 ===
{{quote box|width=220px|quote=即使这东方－西方、游戏－电影、动画－动作的宏大结合未获成功，我们仍会铭记这真正CG演员诞生的时刻。|source=《时代》杂志<ref name="time" />}}

在电影上映之前，已有声音对其商业成功表示怀疑；《[[时代|时代]]》杂志的克里斯·泰勒称，此前已有电子游戏改编作创不佳票房的记录，而本片仅仅是坂口的首部故事片<ref name="time" />。电影于2001年7月2日在美国加利福尼亚洛杉矶曼恩布鲁因斯剧院（{{lang|en|Mann Bruins Theater}}）首映，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.seeing-stars.com/Meet/MoviePremierePressReleases/FinalFantasy.shtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110001333/http://www.seeing-stars.com/Meet/MoviePremierePressReleases/FinalFantasy.shtml |archivedate=2014-11-10 |title=Advisory/The World Premiere of Columbia Pictures & Square Pictures' "Final Fantasy" |date=2001-06-28 |work=Seeing Stars |accessdate=2015-01-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>并于7月11日在美国上映。电影北美票房收入3,200万美元，全球票房总额为8,500万美元<ref name="Boxofficemojo" />。电影在多数东南亚地区票房一般或不佳；但在澳大利亚、新西兰和韩国表现良好<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2001/film/news/b-o-s-animal-planet-1117850492/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128133501/http://variety.com/2001/film/news/b-o-s-animal-planet-1117850492/ |archivedate=2015-01-28 |title=B.O.'s animal planet |last=Groves |first=Don |date=2001-07-30 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=2014-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{le|Boston.com|Boston.com}}在2006年将其列为第四大[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]，在映毕后估计损失超过9,400万美元<ref name=bomb/>。[[CNBC|CNBC]]在2012年3月称《灵魂深处》为第9大票房炸弹<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/38815985/page/9 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130141100/http://www.cnbc.com/id/38815985/page/9 |archivedate=2015-01-30 |title=The 15 Biggest Box Office Bombs |last=Bukszpan |first=Daniel |date=2012-03-20 |work=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |accessdate=2012-01-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但《时代》同日公布的十大票房失败榜单中无本片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://business.time.com/2012/03/21/the-top-ten-biggest-money-losing-movies-of-all-time/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025015440/http://business.time.com/2012/03/21/the-top-ten-biggest-money-losing-movies-of-all-time/ |archivedate=2014-10-25 |title=The Top 10 Biggest Money-Losing Movies of All Time |last=Matthews |first=Christopher |date=2012-03-20 |work=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |accessdate=2012-01-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 媒体评论 ===
在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]的143个评论中，《灵魂深处》获得44%的积极评价，评论共同的看法是电影“提高了电脑动画电影的标准，但故事平淡且缺乏情感”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_fantasy_the_spirits_within/ |title=Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within (2001) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2010-08-01 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004213021/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_fantasy_the_spirits_within/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[MetaCritic|MetaCritic]]收集28个专业评论的加权得分也为49/100<ref name="MetaCritic">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/final-fantasy-the-spirits-within|title=Overview over ''Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within'' reviews|accessdate=2007-07-23|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|archive-date=2011-08-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60fg8oU5G?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/final-fantasy-the-spirits-within|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影获[[金卷轴奖|金卷轴奖]]之“最佳音效剪辑－动画长篇”以及[[影评人协会|影评人协会]]的“最佳动画唱片”提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mpse.org/history/history.html |title=Motion Picture Sound Editors: Who We Are |publisher=[[Motion_Picture_Sound_Editors|Motion Picture Sound Editors]]/ [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] |accessdate=2010-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100301053153/http://www.mpse.org/history/history.html |archive-date=2010-03-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ofcs.rottentomatoes.com/pages/awards/2001nominees |title=OFCS Awards for 2001 Nominees |publisher=[[Online_Film_Critics_Society|Online Film Critics Society]] |accessdate=2010-05-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509073145/http://ofcs.rottentomatoes.com/pages/awards/2001nominees |archivedate=2008-05-09 }} ,</ref>，但皆未获奖。

[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]对《灵魂深处》表示大力支持，打出了3.5/4星，并赞扬电影为“技术里程碑”，但他也承认电影基本情节缺少“如[[史蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格|史蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格]]《[[人工智能_(电影)|人工智能]]》那样的智慧和胆量”。他称他虽然从没有坚信“逼真”的阿琪·罗斯是真实人类的感觉，但他又称，她创作者“敢于激我们去欣赏他们的技巧。如果阿琪并非和人类演员一样真实，她就如修饰光泽完美的[[玩伴女郎|玩伴女郎]]的人类。”<ref name="ebertbook">{{cite book |title=Roger Ebert's Movie Yearbook 2004 |url=https://archive.org/details/rogerebertsmovi00eber |last=Ebert |first=Roger |authorlink=Roger Ebert |year=2003 |publisher=Andrews McMeel Publishing |isbn=0-7407-3834-8 |page=[https://archive.org/details/rogerebertsmovi00eber/page/216 216]}}</ref>他还表示他渴望电影成功，以期望看到更多以此画面制作的电影，但他对电影能力的是否被接受表示怀疑<ref>{{cite news |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20010711/REVIEWS/107110301/1023 |title=Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within (PG-13) |author=Ebert, Roger |date=2001-07-11 |work=Chicago Sun-Times |publisher= |accessdate=2010-02-03 |archive-date=2009-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620013901/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20010711%2FREVIEWS%2F107110301%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 对阿琪·罗斯的评价 ===

《娱乐周刊》将阿琪称为“{{le|时髦女郎|It girl}}”，并称“将这栩栩如生的女主人公叫动画，就如将[[林布蘭|林布蘭]]叫涂鸦”<ref>{{cite web | author=Staff | title=The It List 2001;Aki | url=http://www.ew.com/ew/itlist/2001/7.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010625105611/http://www.ew.com/ew/itlist/2001/7.html | work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | archivedate=2001-06-25 | accessdate=2009-05-27 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在《[[Maxim|Maxim]]》举办的最性感女郎读者票选中，阿琪在100人中位列87，是首个登上榜单的虚构人物，此外她还出现在当期的封面上<ref name="nyt">{{cite news |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F00E7D81038F935A35756C0A9679C8B63 |title=Perfect Model: Gorgeous, No Complaints, Made of Pixels |accessdate=2008-01-26 |author=Ruth La Ferla |date=2001-05-06 |pages=9–1 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |publisher=[[The_New_York_Times_Company|The New York Times Company]] |archive-date=2008-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205030323/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F00E7D81038F935A35756C0A9679C8B63 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的外貌获得积极评价<ref>{{cite news |author=Gumbel, Andrew |title=Hollywood finds the perfect star: Tall, attractive, and guaranteed not to strike |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/hollywood-finds-the-perfect-star--tall-attractive-and-guaranteed-not-to-strike-685474.html |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |publisher=[[Independent_News_&_Media|Independent News & Media]] |location=London |date=2001-05-21 |accessdate=2008-01-26 |archive-date=2009-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091207081801/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/hollywood-finds-the-perfect-star--tall-attractive-and-guaranteed-not-to-strike-685474.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，评论称赞了头发渲染等细节精密的角色模型<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/triplej/review/film/s350149.htm |title=Final Fantasy: The Spirit's Within |accessdate=2008-01-26 |author=Spencer, Megan |work=[[Triple_J|Triple J]] |publisher=[[Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Australian Broadcasting Corporation]] |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216070609/http://www.abc.net.au/triplej/review/film/s350149.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》形容她有[[異形_(電影系列)|《异形》系列]]角色{{le|埃伦·里普利|Ellen Ripley}}{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=858,2348}}|group="注释"}}“血肉丰满的效果”，以及《[[永不妥协|永不妥协]]》中[[茱莉亚·罗伯茨|茱莉亚·罗伯茨]]的视觉魅力<ref name="nyt" />。赫维·费希尔（{{lang|en|Herve Fischer}}{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=1266,953}}|group="注释"}}在《数字冲击：面对新现实》（{{lang|en|Digital Shock: Confronting the New Reality}}）一书中称阿琪是有着“令人印象深刻美貌”的虚拟女演员，并将其和电子游戏角色[[劳拉·克劳馥|劳拉·克劳馥]]做了对比<ref>{{cite book |title=Roger Ebert's Movie Yearbook 2004 |last=Fischer |first=Hervé |author2=Rhonda Mullins |year=2006 |publisher=McGill-Queen's Press – MQUP |isbn=0-7735-3114-9 |page=96}}</ref>。与此相反，利维娅·莫内（{{lang|en|Livia Monnet}}）{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=1698,1918}}|group="注释"}}在《机器人幽灵和连线梦想》（{{lang|en|Robot Ghosts and Wired Dreams: Japanese Science Fiction from Origins to Anime}}）里以日本电影中不断被绑架的女子做比方，批评了她的特征，并继续将其存在“淡化”，称其之代表着计算机生成角色，“一个没有真正所指，设想的女性影片角色”<ref>{{cite book |title=Robot Ghosts and Wired Dreams: Japanese Science Fiction from Origins to Anime |pages=209–211 |publisher=[[University_of_Minnesota|University of Minnesota Press]] |year=2007 |author=Bolton, Christopher |author2=Istvan Csicsery-Ronay Jr., Takayuki Tatsumi |isbn=0-8166-4974-X}}</ref>。《动作与冒险电影》（{{lang|en|Action and Adventure Cinema}}）的作者马克·奥戴（{{lang|en|Marc O'Day}}）{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=1791,2037}}|group="注释"}}形容她是科幻电影中“至少公开引起性欲”的女性角色，但书也认为她是[[海报女郎|海报女郎]]类角色处理方式的例子之一，“转变为性欲幻想机器”<ref>{{cite book |title=Action and Adventure Cinema |author=Tasker, Yvonne |publisher=Routledge |year=2004 |isbn=0-415-23506-5}}</ref>。<!-- ''Media Matrix: Sexing the New Reality'' noted the emphasis by her creators on making her appear real, though questioned the portrayal of her character, in particular if the presence of her unconsciousness in the film was intended as a means to have the character appear more human to viewers.<ref>{{cite book |title=Media Matrix: Sexing the New Reality |url=https://archive.org/details/mediamatrixsexin00cree |publisher=Allen & Unwin |year=2003 |author=Creed, Barbara |pages=[https://archive.org/details/mediamatrixsexin00cree/page/n168 161], 167 |isbn=1-86508-926-5}}</ref> -->

=== 影响与跨媒体 ===

据[[艾尼克斯|艾尼克斯]]创办人[[福岛康博|福岛康博]]称，史克威尔和艾尼克斯的合并计划早在2000年就有考虑，但史克威尔因《灵魂深处》的失败而大幅亏损，艾尼克斯产生犹豫而导致合并延迟<ref>{{cite web |last=Long |first=Andrew |year=2003 |work=RPGamer |url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q2-2003/042503e.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113044027/http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q2-2003/042503e.html |archivedate=2014-11-13 |title=Square-Enix Gives Chrono Break Trademark Some Playmates |accessdate=2014-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。史克威尔影业在2002年1月下旬宣布关闭，重要原因是《灵魂深处》的商业失败<ref name=briscoe />。

电影CGI效果相对顺利的用于后来的电影，如[[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]的2009年电影《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》<ref>{{cite web |last=Child |first=Ben |title=Avatar: a first look at the trailer for James Cameron's 3D spectacular |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2009/aug/21/avatar-first-trailer-james-cameron-3d |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303011340/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2009/aug/21/avatar-first-trailer-james-cameron-3d |archivedate=2014-03-03 |date=2009-08-21 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=2014-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Usher |first=William |title=AMD Says Xbox 720 Will Have Avatar Quality Graphics |date=2011-07-17 |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/games/AMD-Says-Xbox-720-Have-Avatar-Quality-Graphics-33537.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224235928/http://www.cinemablend.com/games/AMD-Says-Xbox-720-Have-Avatar-Quality-Graphics-33537.html |archivedate=2014-02-24 |work=Cinema Blend |accessdate=2014-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[BioWare|BioWare]]艺术总监德里克·沃茨（{{lang|en|Derek Watts}}）{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=736,2956}}|group="注释"}}在2011年称，《灵魂深处》是影响[[动作角色扮演游戏|动作角色扮演游戏]]系列[[质量效应|质量效应]]成功的重要因素<ref>{{cite web |last=Hussain |first=Tamoor |title=BioWare: Mass Effect inspired 'a lot' by Final Fantasy film: Art director discusses "great" influences |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/309198/bioware-mass-effect-inspired-a-lot-by-final-fantasy-film/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228010247/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/309198/bioware-mass-effect-inspired-a-lot-by-final-fantasy-film/ |archivedate=2014-12-28 |work=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]] |date=2011-06-27 |accessdate=2014-12-23 |10= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

虽然《灵魂深处》零散改编自游戏，但电影本身从无改编回游戏的计划。坂口表示此因当时游戏硬件能力有限，任何改编游戏的图形都远落后于电影本身<ref name=dream/>。

由{{le|迪安·韦斯利·史密斯|Dean Wesley Smith}}{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=706,2965,2580}}|group="注释"}}改编的小说由[[Pocket_Books|Pocket Books]]于2001年6月出版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/dp/0743424190/ |title=Final Fantasy : The Spirits Within (Mass Market Paperback) |work=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] |accessdate=2010-05-12 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629133248/http://www.amazon.com/dp/0743424190/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。配套书《最终幻想：灵魂深处的幕后》（{{lang|en|''The Making of Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within''}}）由[[BradyGames|BradyGames]]于2001年8月出版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/dp/0744000718/ |title=The Making of Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within |work=[[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] |accessdate=2010-05-12 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629133305/http://www.amazon.com/dp/0744000718/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该书为240页全彩，由{{le|史蒂文·L·肯特|Steven L. Kent}}{{#tag:ref|译名参考自《世界人名翻译大辞典》。{{Sfn|新华社译名室|1993|p=2639,1473}}|group="注释"}}编辑，其中收录由导演坂口博信的前言，以及电影各方面的创作信息，包括概念创作图、故事板、布景与道具、动作捕捉与动画，以及全[[剧本|脚本]]的草稿<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesfirst.com/reviews/monica/ff_swbook/ff_swbook.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229155156/http://www.gamesfirst.com/reviews/monica/ff_swbook/ff_swbook.htm |archivedate=2012-02-29 |title=The Making of Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within |last=Hafer |first=Monica |date=2001-09-10 |work=GamesFirst! |accessdate=2014-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

